I've ever celebrated.

801
01:25:54,714 --> 01:25:56,192
That's not true.

802
01:25:56,216 --> 01:25:58,820
Yes, it is.
My first party on the day.

803
01:25:58,844 --> 01:26:01,136
That's unusual.

804
01:26:03,557 --> 01:26:06,953
