- That's great!
- I haven't finished.

830
01:29:32,307 --> 01:29:35,517
Abracadabra!

831
01:29:38,021 --> 01:29:39,813
How did you do that?

832
01:29:45,111 --> 01:29:46,881
Come here, you.

833
01:29:46,905 --> 01:29:48,113
Come here.

834
01:29:58,583 --> 01:30:01,168
Happy birthday, sweetheart.

